text: Komsomolsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Karanovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 177 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 13 km from Karan-Kunkas. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Komsomolsky, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
